initialed by both of you.

18:53.007 --> 18:54.550
No problem.

18:54.550 --> 18:57.803
Okay. Yeah.

18:57.803 --> 19:00.973
What's this
required monitoring thing?

19:00.973 --> 19:02.725
Um, Section 8B?

19:02.725 --> 19:04.977
