from the Foundation.

19:04.977 --> 19:07.104
We'll stop by and bring you
diapers, clothes,

19:07.104 --> 19:09.273
whatever you need.

19:09.273 --> 19:11.650
See? Yeah. That's nice.

19:11.650 --> 19:13.569
