Here.

20:28.686 --> 20:30.020
It's lace.

20:30.020 --> 20:31.355
Put it in your windows.

20:31.355 --> 20:36.318
It will help fortify
the light in your home.

20:36.318 --> 20:37.570
Okay.

20:37.570 --> 20:40.698
For your red wine.

20:40.698 --> 20:42.074
