one of the representatives

20:54.587 --> 20:57.923
through out app.

20:57.923 --> 21:00.676
Here's the login information.

21:00.676 --> 21:03.095
-You guys have an app?
-Of course!

21:03.095 --> 21:06.807
Magic isn't stuck
in the dark ages.

21:06.807 --> 21:08.893
The app's got all the rules

21:08.893 --> 21:12.980
and a section for your
prayers and pronunciations,

21:12.980 --> 21:14.523
my contact info.

21:14.523 --> 21:17.234
But just use
the chat function.

21:17.234 --> 21:18.360
They can help.

21:18.360 --> 21:20.154
And, frankly,
they know the little things

21:20.154 --> 21:21.447
better than I do.

21:21.447 --> 21:24.033
If you need to delay
for any reason, that's fine.

21:24.033 --> 21:27.453
But if you cheat
and don't tell me...

21:27.453 --> 21:31.081
Anything unexpected
can be a disaster.

21:31.081 --> 21:34.960
Hm. Okay, well, we'll behave.

21:34.960 --> 21:37.421
You'd better.

21:37.421 --> 21:40.132
Now. Before you begin
this journey,

21:40.132 --> 21:44.678
take a night, get drunk,
eat junk food, get high.

21:44.678 --> 21:47.515
Enjoy what you're sacrificing.

21:47.515 --> 21:49.808
Understand it.

21:49.808 --> 21:53.521
I'm so happy for you both!

21:53.521 --> 21:58.567
♪

21:58.567 --> 22:00.152
Come on, open up, open up.

22:00.152 --> 22:01.362
-Uh-uh.
-Just practice, rehearsal.

22:01.362 --> 22:03.155
We're gonna have a baby,
open up.

22:03.155 --> 22:05.491
