-Uh-uh...uh-uh...

22:05.491 --> 22:08.452
(crunching)

22:08.452 --> 22:10.246
I can't believe
we're doing this.

22:10.246 --> 22:12.998
♪

22:12.998 --> 22:15.125
I don't wanna go a month
without processed carbs.

22:15.125 --> 22:17.503
♪

22:17.503 --> 22:18.671
So you're in?

22:18.671 --> 22:19.880
100 percent.

22:19.880 --> 22:21.966
You're not gonna
accidentally eat a cookie

22:21.966 --> 22:24.677
every two and a half weeks?

22:24.677 --> 22:25.803
No!

22:25.803 --> 22:26.804
Hm.

22:26.804 --> 22:30.432
♪

22:30.432 --> 22:33.894
Plus, it's easier than IVF,
and cheaper.

22:33.894 --> 22:36.897
We could diet a little
and put lace on our windows.

22:36.897 --> 22:38.107
And no shots.

22:38.107 --> 22:41.443
♪

22:41.443 --> 22:44.947
I think this'll be good for us.

22:44.947 --> 22:47.283
