22:47.283 --> 22:49.577
Maybe she can do magic.

22:49.577 --> 22:51.328
She could be like Madam Pomfrey,

22:51.328 --> 22:55.165
who went rogue
to help Muggles.

22:55.165 --> 22:57.293
The next time she's here,

22:57.293 --> 23:00.337
let's say "Voldemort."

23:00.337 --> 23:01.922
See if she flinches.

23:01.922 --> 23:04.133
-That's good, huh?
-That's good.

23:04.133 --> 23:05.509
Fuckin' brilliant.

23:05.509 --> 23:07.761
Dude, I think weed
makes me smarter.

23:07.761 --> 23:12.891
Ra-dara nu...

23:12.891 --> 23:14.435
come on.

23:14.435 --> 23:19.940
Nu-ka ko-poer

23:19.940 --> 23:22.484
e son.

23:22.484 --> 23:24.194
Again.

23:24.194 --> 23:25.863
Excuse me.

23:25.863 --> 23:27.114
Ugh, I'm gonna be late.

23:27.114 --> 23:30.743
♪

23:30.743 --> 23:33.829
