24:16.080 --> 24:18.499
You ready for tomorrow?

24:18.499 --> 24:21.210
I'm ready for this to be done.

24:21.210 --> 24:24.630
Sick of eating rabbit food.

24:24.630 --> 24:29.718
And I miss, you know, sex.

24:29.718 --> 24:32.054
Same...

24:32.054 --> 24:34.723
