24:34.723 --> 24:37.434
Um...

24:37.434 --> 24:42.064
If this, um, doesn't work,

24:42.064 --> 24:44.900
are you gonna be okay?

24:44.900 --> 24:47.403
(insects chirring)

24:49.071 --> 24:51.490
I think so.

24:51.490 --> 24:53.992
I can't get any crazier
than this, right?

24:53.992 --> 24:58.038
Hmph. Promise?

24:58.038 --> 24:59.289
Promise.

25:17.558 --> 25:20.811
Wonderful.
Now we can begin.

25:20.811 --> 25:24.440
-I just wanna say, we're so--
-I'll be right back.

25:24.440 --> 25:27.818
Wow.

25:27.818 --> 25:33.741
Well, whatever happens,
it will be a hell of a story.

25:33.741 --> 25:35.242
Seriously.

25:43.667 --> 25:45.461
Do you, uh,
do you want some help?

25:45.461 --> 25:46.587
Oh, no, no, no.

25:46.587 --> 25:48.380
I've got it, sweetie.

25:52.050 --> 25:54.470
Is this baby bondage gear?

25:54.470 --> 25:56.930
What do you think
these lightbulbs are for?

25:56.930 --> 25:58.223
The baby will have
sensitive eyes

25:58.223 --> 25:59.683
from the magic.

25:59.683 --> 26:03.854
Six months, you won't even
be able to tell at all.

26:03.854 --> 26:05.105
Okay.

26:11.236 --> 26:12.905
(car alarm chirps)

26:23.582 --> 26:25.501
Let's get to it.

26:25.501 --> 26:27.377
