36:40.031 --> 36:42.325
Now, please, strip nude.

36:42.325 --> 36:50.208
♪

36:50.208 --> 36:51.960
How did you think it worked?

36:51.960 --> 36:55.880
♪

36:55.880 --> 36:58.967
I guess, uh,
just pretend like

36:58.967 --> 37:00.552
we're on that beach
from our honeymoon?

37:00.552 --> 37:02.679
Are you gonna get sunburn
on your junk again?

37:02.679 --> 37:04.431
Nice.

37:04.431 --> 37:08.935
Man and woman
is all there is.

37:08.935 --> 37:11.855
I am outside your world.

37:11.855 --> 37:13.857
Your world is a void.

37:13.857 --> 37:16.109
All you see is each other,

37:16.109 --> 37:18.903
bathing in the light
of your love,

37:18.903 --> 37:22.699
the light between the stars.

37:22.699 --> 37:24.492
Don't think about me.

37:24.492 --> 37:27.287
Don't think about
making a child.

37:27.287 --> 37:29.247
This doesn't work
in our world.

37:29.247 --> 37:33.668
It only works in the world
you create together.

37:33.668 --> 37:39.132
The symbols I'm drawing
will bind you in that world.

37:39.132 --> 37:42.427
So let your eyes be honest.

37:42.427 --> 37:44.637
Look at each other.

37:44.637 --> 37:46.139
Take it in.

37:46.139 --> 37:48.600
♪

37:48.600 --> 37:54.314
Think about everything
your partner has given you.

37:54.314 --> 37:57.066
Every smile,
every laugh,

37:57.066 --> 37:59.736
every flutter
of your heart.

37:59.736 --> 38:01.446
Place your palms together,

38:01.446 --> 38:02.864
and through your touch,

38:02.864 --> 38:06.201
show your partner
the person they are to you.

38:06.201 --> 38:07.785
Interlock your fingers

38:07.785 --> 38:10.997
and become the person
you are to them.

38:10.997 --> 38:12.332
You are connected.

38:12.332 --> 38:15.251
You are alone
in your world.

38:15.251 --> 38:16.920
Hold fast.

38:16.920 --> 38:19.005
Stay together.

38:19.005 --> 38:20.381
Don't let go.

38:20.381 --> 38:23.718
♪

38:23.718 --> 38:26.221
(chanting in foreign language)

38:26.221 --> 38:30.141
Give yourself to her.

38:30.141 --> 38:32.185
They await you.

38:32.185 --> 38:34.854
Your light.

38:34.854 --> 38:37.357
Be known to them,

38:37.357 --> 38:40.401
O great ones!

38:40.401 --> 38:43.363
(echoed incantation)

38:43.363 --> 38:47.033
♪

38:47.033 --> 38:50.411
Come to them!

38:50.411 --> 38:53.122
(rumbling)

38:53.122 --> 38:59.003
♪

38:59.003 --> 39:00.672
You did well.

39:00.672 --> 39:02.215
I hope it worked.

39:02.215 --> 39:04.551
But we'll know for sure
in the morning.

39:04.551 --> 39:06.094
Get some rest.

39:06.094 --> 39:07.679
I'll clean up.

39:07.679 --> 39:17.689
♪

39:18.523 --> 39:21.192
(birdsong)

39:21.192 --> 39:26.781
♪

39:26.781 --> 39:28.575
(groaning)

39:28.575 --> 39:31.119
Holy shit!

39:31.119 --> 39:32.787
Oh, God.

39:32.787 --> 39:36.874
♪

39:36.874 --> 39:38.918
-Good morning.
-Oh!

39:38.918 --> 39:40.545
Sit, sit.

39:40.545 --> 39:41.713
Morning.

39:41.713 --> 39:44.424
-Sleep well?
-Uggh.

39:44.424 --> 39:48.428
Well, some breakfast
should perk you up.

39:48.428 --> 39:50.930
(liquid being poured)

39:52.432 --> 39:55.768
Thanks.

39:55.768 --> 39:57.520
(glasses clink)

40:23.463 --> 40:25.256
Mm.

40:25.256 --> 40:27.050
Um...

40:27.050 --> 40:28.217
What?

40:28.217 --> 40:29.761
Mm...

40:29.761 --> 40:31.220
That's a good sign.

40:31.220 --> 40:34.182
Come with me.

40:34.182 --> 40:36.643
Eat it all, okay?

40:36.643 --> 40:38.561
Okay...

40:42.857 --> 40:44.359
(door closes)

40:44.359 --> 40:46.569
This will be uncomfortable,

40:46.569 --> 40:48.446
but you'll feel better.

40:48.446 --> 40:52.700
It won't last too long,
I promise.

40:52.700 --> 40:56.454
(Ola sings in foreign language
while Makayla retches)

41:16.933 --> 41:19.435
(softly exclaiming)

41:21.521 --> 41:24.023
(toilet flushes)

41:28.695 --> 41:30.905
I think it worked.

41:30.905 --> 41:33.199
The toilet?

41:33.199 --> 41:36.494
I'm pregnant!

41:36.494 --> 41:38.496
How could you possibly
know that?

41:38.496 --> 41:39.831
-Ola said that--
-An egg can't implant

41:39.831 --> 41:41.165
that quickly.

41:41.165 --> 41:42.750
Of course it can.

41:42.750 --> 41:45.169
I'm only here for a week,
not nine months.

41:45.169 --> 41:47.714
♪

41:47.714 --> 41:49.841
Wait, wait,
so, in a week...

41:49.841 --> 41:51.175
She'll have a baby

41:51.175 --> 41:52.760
and I'll be out of your hair.

41:52.760 --> 41:55.596
(nervous laughter)

41:55.596 --> 41:58.182
What? No, that's not, that's--

41:58.182 --> 41:59.308
It's magic.

41:59.308 --> 42:01.269
I've been telling you.

42:01.269 --> 42:03.896
Why do you think
she's nauseous?

42:03.896 --> 42:05.148
Food poisoning?

42:05.148 --> 42:06.357
-Eric.
-What?

42:06.357 --> 42:09.485
I can feel it.

42:09.485 --> 42:11.571
A week?

42:11.571 --> 42:14.741
How is that a bad thing?

42:14.741 --> 42:16.784
Honey...

42:16.784 --> 42:19.036
Oh---uh, no, no.

42:19.036 --> 42:28.212
♪

42:28.212 --> 42:29.964
Let's get you to bed.

42:29.964 --> 42:32.467
(toilet flushes)

42:34.302 --> 42:36.804
(birdsong)

42:51.903 --> 42:53.404
She's doing great.

42:53.404 --> 42:55.323
This is perfectly normal.

42:55.323 --> 42:57.700
There's a lot going on
inside of her.

43:01.412 --> 43:03.873
I don't know if I get
paternity leave at work

43:03.873 --> 43:05.500
with no notice.

43:05.500 --> 43:07.418
Oh, don't worry
about all that!

43:07.418 --> 43:09.545
The Foundation can help.

43:09.545 --> 43:11.380
Let's keep you busy.

43:21.098 --> 43:23.184
Wow. Mancala.

43:23.184 --> 43:24.936
It's been a while.

43:24.936 --> 43:29.315
It's easy.
You'll remember fast.

43:29.315 --> 43:31.651
Me again.

43:31.651 --> 43:34.779
(beans clattering)

43:34.779 --> 43:36.113
I just keep waiting
for you to pull out

43:36.113 --> 43:37.824
a vacuum to sell me.

43:37.824 --> 43:39.951
Oh, I promise you,

43:39.951 --> 43:42.620
that's not what
the Gravida Foundation is about.

43:42.620 --> 43:45.706
But obviously, you know,
they want something.

43:45.706 --> 43:47.291
To bring life
into the world,

43:47.291 --> 43:50.419
that's all.

43:50.419 --> 43:54.674
When you went from barren
to a mother in a week,

43:54.674 --> 43:57.260
which is insane,

43:57.260 --> 44:00.137
what'd you tell people?

44:00.137 --> 44:01.722
They'll just be happy for you.

44:01.722 --> 44:04.267
♪

44:04.267 --> 44:05.977
And after you had your son,

44:05.977 --> 44:09.063
well, I mean, do a lot
of the kids that they make--

44:09.063 --> 44:10.648
'cause they do make them--

44:10.648 --> 44:13.150
um, do they all
become doctors?

44:13.150 --> 44:14.777
I mean, your son is one,
and Dr. Z.

44:14.777 --> 44:16.153
Some.

44:16.153 --> 44:17.822
The Foundation
wants their children

44:17.822 --> 44:19.824
to reach their full potential,

44:19.824 --> 44:22.743
whatever they want to be.

44:22.743 --> 44:25.204
We're a family.

44:25.204 --> 44:28.666
And you'll be
a part of it.

44:28.666 --> 44:30.835
The doctor said that too.

44:30.835 --> 44:32.295
He would know.

44:32.295 --> 44:38.050
♪

44:38.050 --> 44:40.928
I'm so hungry!

44:40.928 --> 44:43.139
(Ola chants in foreign language)

44:43.139 --> 44:46.267
(Makayla slurps food
and makes relishing noises)

44:46.267 --> 44:52.565
♪

44:52.565 --> 44:54.233
Just ignore me.

44:54.233 --> 44:59.155
♪

44:59.155 --> 45:00.781
Like I said,

45:00.781 --> 45:02.533
you guys are doing great.

45:02.533 --> 45:03.993
This week's gonna be tough,

45:03.993 --> 45:06.120
but just keep eating
what Ola feeds you.

45:06.120 --> 45:07.788
Sure thing.

45:10.207 --> 45:12.376
How long have you known Ola?

45:12.376 --> 45:14.170
Oh, we go way back,

45:14.170 --> 45:17.340
since she started
the Foundation.

45:17.340 --> 45:18.633
Really?

45:18.633 --> 45:21.135
Because she said

45:21.135 --> 45:23.429
she started with them
when she had her son.

45:23.429 --> 45:25.306
Yeah, that's true.

45:25.306 --> 45:27.892
She said her son
just turned 40.

45:27.892 --> 45:29.644
Did she?

45:29.644 --> 45:31.979
She did.

45:31.979 --> 45:33.230
Do you know what
she could have been talk--

45:33.230 --> 45:35.733
-Eric, please!
-See you guys tomorrow.

45:40.905 --> 45:42.949
(door opens, closes)

45:42.949 --> 45:52.959
♪

45:53.167 --> 45:55.962
(Makayla exclaims,
baby cries)

45:55.962 --> 45:58.589
♪

45:58.589 --> 46:01.050
(scream)

46:01.050 --> 46:02.510
Makayla?

46:02.510 --> 46:04.095
(Makayla pants, exclaims)

46:04.095 --> 46:05.680
(groaning)

46:05.680 --> 46:07.014
Why were you screaming?

46:07.014 --> 46:08.808
-It hurts.
-There's blood.

46:08.808 --> 46:11.018
Oh, there's always blood.

46:11.018 --> 46:13.270
Did you oil
like you were supposed to?

46:13.270 --> 46:14.313
Uh-huh.

46:14.313 --> 46:18.109
The baby's doing nine months
of growing in one week.

46:18.109 --> 46:20.486
The skin can split
a little bit.

46:20.486 --> 46:23.739
(groaning)

46:23.739 --> 46:25.783
You're fine, you're fine.

46:25.783 --> 46:28.452
It's okay, it's okay.

46:28.452 --> 46:30.204
♪

46:30.204 --> 46:31.539
I'm calling 9-1-1.

46:31.539 --> 46:33.874
They won't have any idea
what to do with this.

46:33.874 --> 46:36.293
Yeah, but...

46:36.293 --> 46:37.837
Holy shit.

46:37.837 --> 46:41.090
(groaning)

46:41.090 --> 46:43.092
Come on, let's clean you up.

46:43.092 --> 46:44.844
Are you sure we should move her?

46:44.844 --> 46:46.470
Yes, give her a hand.

46:46.470 --> 46:47.722
♪

46:47.722 --> 46:48.848
Honey?

46:48.848 --> 46:52.101
♪

46:52.101 --> 46:53.811
(groans)

46:53.811 --> 46:55.187
Come on.

46:55.187 --> 46:58.024
♪

46:58.024 --> 47:00.401
Relax, dear, this is common.

47:00.401 --> 47:02.820
-Then why didn't you warn us?
-It's okay, Eric.

47:02.820 --> 47:05.031
This whole process
is scary enough.

47:05.031 --> 47:07.533
It's better for the baby
if you're not all anxious

47:07.533 --> 47:08.951
about every detail.

47:08.951 --> 47:11.203
-I'm gonna call the doctor.
-Sure, if you'd like,

47:11.203 --> 47:14.081
but he's gonna tell you
the same thing I did.

47:14.081 --> 47:18.461
♪

47:18.461 --> 47:20.337
(phone dialing)

47:20.337 --> 47:22.923
-Hello, Dr. Zekeny.
-Hey, Dr. Z.

47:22.923 --> 47:25.301
-It's Eric Galleston.
-Hey, Eric, how are ya?

47:25.301 --> 47:27.762
Not very good, actually.

47:27.762 --> 47:30.306
Makayla just woke up
with her stomach split open,

47:30.306 --> 47:33.392
and...and then she started
licking her own blood.

47:33.392 --> 47:34.935
It's nothing to worry about.

47:34.935 --> 47:36.270
I know it's super scary,

47:36.270 --> 47:39.315
but this is all part
of the process, I promise.

47:39.315 --> 47:42.276
These are--these are
all good signs.

47:42.276 --> 47:44.779
-What about the licking?
-Weird cravings.

47:44.779 --> 47:47.448
Yeah, I had a patient once
who kept wanting to drink

47:47.448 --> 47:49.241
window cleaner.

47:49.241 --> 47:50.993
I'll see you tomorrow night.

47:50.993 --> 47:54.789
♪

47:54.789 --> 47:58.000
Oh, I remember what it's like.

47:58.000 --> 48:01.128
But you knew pregnancy
would be hard.

48:01.128 --> 48:03.756
Aren't we lucky
ours are so fast?

48:03.756 --> 48:05.299
(groaning)

48:05.299 --> 48:08.844
Oh, don't make it harder
for the baby too.

48:08.844 --> 48:12.306
The process is working.

48:12.306 --> 48:14.225
It's what you wanted.

48:14.225 --> 48:22.108
♪

48:22.108 --> 48:24.401
Hey, are you okay?

48:24.401 --> 48:28.322
We got her all wrapped up
with some special bandages.

48:28.322 --> 48:30.658
I'm wonderful.

48:30.658 --> 48:32.743
You're gonna be a dad.

48:32.743 --> 48:40.543
♪

48:40.543 --> 48:43.003
(soft groaning)

48:43.003 --> 48:47.424
♪

48:47.424 --> 48:48.843
(sighs)

48:48.843 --> 48:55.975
♪

48:55.975 --> 48:58.978
You two lovebirds sleep tight.

48:58.978 --> 49:00.312
Thanks, Ola.

49:00.312 --> 49:02.189
(footsteps)

49:02.189 --> 49:04.191
(door opens, closes)

49:04.191 --> 49:14.201
♪

49:38.058 --> 49:40.561
(birds chirping)

49:40.561 --> 49:42.563
♪

49:42.563 --> 49:44.523
Mmm.

49:44.523 --> 49:47.193
How's yours?

49:47.193 --> 49:49.111
I'm not that hungry.

49:49.111 --> 49:51.572
Too bad.
Come on, eat, eat, eat.

49:51.572 --> 49:53.782
Oh!

49:53.782 --> 49:55.618
Ola...

49:55.618 --> 49:57.661
the doctor said
he's been working with you

49:57.661 --> 49:59.455
since you started
with the foundation.

49:59.455 --> 50:00.372
That's right.

50:00.372 --> 50:02.291
Which is when your son was born,

50:02.291 --> 50:04.168
about 40 years ago?

50:04.168 --> 50:06.795
Thirty-seven.

50:06.795 --> 50:10.090
But Zekeny's bio online said
he graduated from med school

50:10.090 --> 50:12.384
in 2002.

50:12.384 --> 50:14.678
Oh, oh, that's right.

50:14.678 --> 50:15.554
(she chuckles)

50:15.554 --> 50:17.806
It was his father who helped me.

50:17.806 --> 50:18.974
Mmm.

50:18.974 --> 50:21.352
I sometimes get them
a bit confused.

50:21.352 --> 50:23.687
Such a family resemblance.

50:23.687 --> 50:27.608
Wouldn't it be cool if your baby
looked just like you?

50:27.608 --> 50:30.444
I'm not naming him Eric Jr.
though.

50:30.444 --> 50:31.737
(laughing)

50:31.737 --> 50:33.864
What was his name?

50:33.864 --> 50:35.407
Zekeny's father.

50:35.407 --> 50:39.203
Um...Abraham, Aaron,
something biblical.

50:39.203 --> 50:41.914
-I like Abraham, or Isaac.
-Zekeny also said it was him,

50:41.914 --> 50:44.333
-not his dad.
-I really like classical names.

50:44.333 --> 50:45.834
Or, ooh, how about Edith?

50:45.834 --> 50:47.461
-Makayla!
-Hey, hey!

50:47.461 --> 50:49.713
Let me talk for one second,
okay?

50:49.713 --> 50:52.132
-All right, I was just excited.
-She's expecting.

50:52.132 --> 50:54.009
Seriously?

50:54.009 --> 50:55.302
(Eric laughs)

50:55.302 --> 50:57.054
What is this?

50:59.515 --> 51:02.268
Oh, no, I guess I'm in trouble.

51:02.268 --> 51:04.853
(birds singing)

51:09.233 --> 51:10.734
It's scary,

51:10.734 --> 51:12.653
it's stressful,
and lots of things--

51:12.653 --> 51:14.571
You guys are hiding something.

51:14.571 --> 51:16.865
He's supposed to be
44 years old, that's bullshit

51:16.865 --> 51:18.325
-and you know it.
-Good Lord!

51:18.325 --> 51:20.828
It's clearly some sort
of miscommunication!

51:20.828 --> 51:22.913
She's pregnant!

51:22.913 --> 51:25.457
You can see that.

51:25.457 --> 51:27.001
Breathe.

51:27.001 --> 51:29.670
Eat.

51:29.670 --> 51:31.463
Be happy.

51:42.099 --> 51:43.851
(sighs, groans)

51:48.856 --> 51:50.399
(sighs)

51:53.777 --> 51:55.070
(groans)

52:00.659 --> 52:02.786
(phone ringing)

52:02.786 --> 52:04.079
(chuckles)

52:04.079 --> 52:06.665
Hey, magic momma, what's up?

52:06.665 --> 52:08.709
It worked.

52:08.709 --> 52:11.128
-I'm pregnant.
-What?

52:11.128 --> 52:12.880
How?

52:12.880 --> 52:14.923
Magic.

52:14.923 --> 52:18.761
Uh, well, that's...wonderful.

52:18.761 --> 52:21.513
Crazy, too, but...

52:21.513 --> 52:23.223
I'm so happy for you.

52:23.223 --> 52:24.266
Thanks.

52:24.266 --> 52:26.143
I wish Eric was as happy.

52:26.143 --> 52:29.438
Well, if he screws this up,
I will fucking kill him.

52:29.438 --> 52:30.856
Please don't.

52:30.856 --> 52:33.567
You know, I was licking blood
off my hand last night.

52:33.567 --> 52:35.486
Yeah, I think that
really freaked Eric out,

52:35.486 --> 52:37.738
but the doctor said
it's just cravings, so...

52:37.738 --> 52:39.782
Wait, wait, wait,
why were you bleeding?

52:39.782 --> 52:42.076
Uh...

52:42.076 --> 52:44.161
The skin on my stomach,

52:44.161 --> 52:47.956
it--it ripped
when it grew so fast.

52:47.956 --> 52:49.416
Jesus.

52:49.416 --> 52:51.543
Well, no wonder Eric's freaked.

52:51.543 --> 52:53.379
Yeah, but...

52:53.379 --> 52:56.715
I know it's weird,
but I'm pregnant.

52:56.715 --> 52:58.342
He should be happy.

52:58.342 --> 53:00.219
Yeah, still...

53:02.137 --> 53:04.056
Okay, um...

53:04.056 --> 53:07.976
If it's real,
I'm sure he'll get there.

53:07.976 --> 53:10.479
-I just know it.
-Thanks.

53:10.479 --> 53:12.689
Really, for everything.

53:12.689 --> 53:16.443
For being a good friend
and for telling us about Susan.

53:16.443 --> 53:20.114
Well, I am a good friend,
but I will not babysit,

53:20.114 --> 53:22.866
but I will hold your beer for
you while you change a diaper.

53:22.866 --> 53:23.784
(chuckles)

53:23.784 --> 53:25.619
Wow, you're so generous.

53:25.619 --> 53:26.870
Love you. Later.

53:26.870 --> 53:28.539
Love you.

53:35.671 --> 53:36.755
(phone dialing)

53:36.755 --> 53:39.049
-Cherise.
-Hey, cuz.

53:39.049 --> 53:41.176
-Can I talk to you about--
-Did she do it?

53:41.176 --> 53:42.177
(baby crying)

53:42.177 --> 53:43.637
She did, didn't she?

53:43.637 --> 53:46.056
Yeah, Makayla, she's pregnant.

53:46.056 --> 53:49.893
Can you come over in person
just in...case...

53:49.893 --> 53:51.228
(baby crying)

53:51.228 --> 53:52.271
Never mind.

53:52.271 --> 53:54.398
Can you just come over, please?

53:54.398 --> 53:56.900
(baby crying)

53:59.695 --> 54:02.072
(birds chirping)

54:02.072 --> 54:05.200
(chuckling)

54:05.200 --> 54:06.452
(door sliding open)

54:06.452 --> 54:09.163
Someone's at the door,
get rid of him.

54:10.664 --> 54:11.957
(door opens)

54:11.957 --> 54:13.250
Hi! Sorry to bug you.

54:13.250 --> 54:14.793
I'm Rufus
with Rufus Extermination,

54:14.793 --> 54:16.295
and I'm here to protect
your family--

54:16.295 --> 54:17.921
-We're fine, thanks.
-You might be fine,

54:17.921 --> 54:19.256
but do you have any kids?

54:19.256 --> 54:22.426
Not yet, my wife is...
almost due.

54:22.426 --> 54:24.261
-Congratulations!
-Thanks.

54:24.261 --> 54:26.889
Uh, my stuff's not so great
for newborns, so...

54:26.889 --> 54:28.348
Awesome, thanks.

54:31.602 --> 54:34.313
Eric, come in here please.

54:34.313 --> 54:44.323
♪

54:46.074 --> 54:50.412
This will be your child's
safe place in the world,

54:50.412 --> 54:54.458
like a womb where the mother
surrounds the child.

54:54.458 --> 54:56.793
Dad too.

54:56.793 --> 55:00.088
-Hold this.
-Okay.

55:00.088 --> 55:04.218
We'll take a bit of your blood
and mix it with the paint.

55:04.218 --> 55:07.221
You will be all around,

55:07.221 --> 55:09.932
watching, protecting,

55:09.932 --> 55:11.808
part of the light.

55:11.808 --> 55:16.063
♪

55:16.063 --> 55:18.315
Okay, um...

55:18.315 --> 55:20.234
♪

55:20.234 --> 55:22.402
(groaning)

55:22.402 --> 55:25.906
♪

55:25.906 --> 55:28.075
What the hell are you doing?

55:28.075 --> 55:29.993
We only need two drops.

55:29.993 --> 55:32.037
I have a finger stick!

55:32.037 --> 55:33.455
(grumbling)

55:33.455 --> 55:34.831
♪

55:34.831 --> 55:36.375
That's way too much.

55:36.375 --> 55:39.127
Why would you cut
your palm anyway?

55:39.127 --> 55:41.380
-There are far better places--
-Okay, I don't know!

55:41.380 --> 55:42.923
Okay, I don't know, I just--

55:42.923 --> 55:44.424
You said blood, and I thought...

55:44.424 --> 55:47.553
I'll tell you what to do,
then you do it.

55:47.553 --> 55:50.305
Right now, do nothing.

55:50.305 --> 55:58.063
♪

55:58.063 --> 56:01.775
I'm sorry,
I was trying to be supportive.

56:01.775 --> 56:04.236
It was very sweet.

56:04.236 --> 56:06.238
You doin' okay?

56:06.238 --> 56:08.282
Eh, it stings a little.

56:08.282 --> 56:10.284
That's not what I meant.

56:10.284 --> 56:13.078
Yeah, you know, I just...

56:13.078 --> 56:15.205
♪

56:15.205 --> 56:18.041
This is all crazy, you know?

56:18.041 --> 56:19.960
Yeah, I know.

56:19.960 --> 56:27.342
♪

56:27.342 --> 56:30.762
This wrap will heal you
relatively quickly.

56:30.762 --> 56:34.141
It's the same as her belly,
actually.

56:34.141 --> 56:35.809
We match.

56:35.809 --> 56:37.811
Don't do that again.

56:37.811 --> 56:42.149
Next time,
wait for specific instructions.

56:42.149 --> 56:52.159
♪

57:00.917 --> 57:01.918
(clicks)

57:01.918 --> 57:02.919
Now, Makayla,

57:02.919 --> 57:04.921
we'll add your blood to Eric's.

57:04.921 --> 57:06.131
♪

57:06.131 --> 57:07.132
(dripping)

57:07.132 --> 57:08.216
Get the paint can.

57:08.216 --> 57:10.886
I got it, I got it.

57:10.886 --> 57:12.304
(grunts)

57:12.304 --> 57:13.889
-Here?
-Down.

57:13.889 --> 57:23.899
♪

57:26.234 --> 57:27.986
(knife scraping)

57:27.986 --> 57:29.613
For mixing.

57:29.613 --> 57:35.243
♪

57:35.243 --> 57:37.954
(chanting in foreign language)

57:44.461 --> 57:50.592
♪

57:50.592 --> 57:53.220
Eric, it'll be your job
to paint.

57:53.220 --> 57:54.638
♪

57:54.638 --> 57:56.848
Be thorough.

57:56.848 --> 58:00.060
Every spot.

58:00.060 --> 58:02.479
You, with me.

58:02.479 --> 58:11.905
♪

58:11.905 --> 58:12.948
(knocking)

58:12.948 --> 58:14.157
(birds chirping)

58:14.157 --> 58:16.159
(shades clattering)

58:19.621 --> 58:20.831
Come in.

58:20.831 --> 58:23.041
Hey, I wanted to see
if you were okay.

58:23.041 --> 58:26.795
-Were you followed?
-What's wrong, what's going on?

58:26.795 --> 58:28.839
He's hungry.
I can't feed him anymore.

58:28.839 --> 58:31.633
-He's--he's always eating.
-Have you talked to the doctor?

58:31.633 --> 58:33.093
The doctors, they don't--

58:33.093 --> 58:34.928
they're all part of it.

58:34.928 --> 58:36.471
The foundation is everywhere.

58:36.471 --> 58:38.306
You have to tell them
not to trust them.

58:38.306 --> 58:39.933
It's not what they say.

58:39.933 --> 58:42.185
What is it?

58:42.185 --> 58:44.938
Makayla said her pregnancy
was only one week.

58:44.938 --> 58:46.106
Is that true?

58:46.106 --> 58:48.358
You have to get your friend
out of there!

58:48.358 --> 58:49.735
Out of the house.

58:49.735 --> 58:52.154
-Just get her away.
-Why?

58:52.154 --> 58:53.947
What did they do?

58:53.947 --> 58:56.032
(sobbing)

58:56.032 --> 58:59.995
They gave me...a monster.

58:59.995 --> 59:02.456
Okay, where's Mark?

59:02.456 --> 59:03.999
(sobbing)

59:03.999 --> 59:05.000
Mark?

59:05.000 --> 59:06.585
He's got a really good job now.

59:06.585 --> 59:08.378
He works for the foundation now,

59:08.378 --> 59:11.631
but the baby, you see,
I feed the baby.

59:11.631 --> 59:13.967
Could I maybe help you?

59:13.967 --> 59:15.719
He's just hungry.

59:15.719 --> 59:20.348
He's so hungry, and I have
been feeding him, but...

59:20.348 --> 59:22.184
I think...

59:22.184 --> 59:24.603
I think--I think
I'm getting sick again.

59:24.603 --> 59:26.855
He won't drink from me.

59:28.231 --> 59:30.692
(breathing heavily)

59:30.692 --> 59:32.444
You could help.

59:32.444 --> 59:35.322
♪

59:35.322 --> 59:37.866
Could I have some
of your blood?

59:37.866 --> 59:40.118
Please, I just need
a little bit,

59:40.118 --> 59:41.620
just one bottle.

59:41.620 --> 59:45.373
Please, he'll take him
from me if I can't!

59:45.373 --> 59:47.959
(gently shushing)

59:47.959 --> 59:50.796
Put it down.

59:50.796 --> 59:53.673
It's okay.

59:53.673 --> 59:55.926
Put it down.

59:55.926 --> 59:57.385
(sobbing)

59:57.385 --> 59:59.471
You have to get her
out of there,

59:59.471 --> 1:00:01.681
get her away.

1:00:01.681 --> 1:00:05.352
Tell--tell her...

1:00:05.352 --> 1:00:07.437
tell her I'm so sorry.

1:00:07.437 --> 1:00:14.236
♪

1:00:14.236 --> 1:00:17.364
He is just so hungry.

1:00:17.364 --> 1:00:19.074
(crying)

1:00:19.074 --> 1:00:29.084
♪

1:00:32.128 --> 1:00:33.672
(light thunk)

1:00:33.672 --> 1:00:35.215
(groans)

1:00:35.215 --> 1:00:37.008
♪

1:00:37.008 --> 1:00:38.969
Okay, um...

1:00:38.969 --> 1:00:47.811
♪

1:00:47.811 --> 1:00:49.187
Wow.

1:00:49.187 --> 1:00:50.689
(laughs)

1:00:54.651 --> 1:00:56.111
Okay.

1:01:06.496 --> 1:01:08.498
(phone vibrating)

1:01:10.959 --> 1:01:12.377
Hey! What's going on?

1:01:12.377 --> 1:01:14.713
Hey, is Makayla okay?
She didn't pick up.

1:01:14.713 --> 1:01:16.798
Uh, yeah, yeah, she's fine.

1:01:16.798 --> 1:01:18.800
Uh, what's wrong?

1:01:18.800 --> 1:01:22.053
I'm at Susan's and she had an--
I don't know, an episode.

1:01:22.053 --> 1:01:24.514
The place is a mess,
and she kept going on and on

1:01:24.514 --> 1:01:26.850
about the--what's it,
the Godiva Foundation?

1:01:26.850 --> 1:01:28.184
Gravida Foundation.

1:01:28.184 --> 1:01:30.979
Yeah, well, she said
she needed blood for the baby.

1:01:30.979 --> 1:01:32.689
She--she asked me
to fill a bottle

1:01:32.689 --> 1:01:33.982
while holding a knife.

1:01:33.982 --> 1:01:35.150
Holy shit!

1:01:35.150 --> 1:01:38.904
-Eric?
-Uh, uh, one second, one second.

1:01:43.033 --> 1:01:45.493
-Uh, go on.
-Look, I called 9-1-1,

1:01:45.493 --> 1:01:46.995
and some people showed up.

1:01:46.995 --> 1:01:48.455
They're in the back
talking to her,

1:01:48.455 --> 1:01:49.915
but I don't know who they are.

1:01:49.915 --> 1:01:51.833
They're not cops or EMTs.

1:01:51.833 --> 1:01:53.627
They're just...weird.

1:01:53.627 --> 1:01:55.712
Cold hands, black suits.

1:01:55.712 --> 1:01:58.465
Huh, well, I haven't seen
anyone here like that, so...

1:01:58.465 --> 1:02:01.593
I'm just really worried
about Makayla.

1:02:01.593 --> 1:02:02.844
I mean, she's okay.

1:02:02.844 --> 1:02:04.596
I heard her stomach ripped

1:02:04.596 --> 1:02:05.847
and she licked blood?

1:02:05.847 --> 1:02:08.475
Eric, that is not normal.

1:02:08.475 --> 1:02:11.436
No, but, uh, she's pregnant.

1:02:11.436 --> 1:02:14.481
Cherise, it's, um...

1:02:14.481 --> 1:02:17.108
-It's real.
-What is real?

1:02:17.108 --> 1:02:21.112
Exactly what kind of baby
are you getting?

1:02:21.112 --> 1:02:23.740
Look, I hope I'm wrong.

1:02:23.740 --> 1:02:27.452
Just...keep an eye out, okay?

1:02:27.452 --> 1:02:29.454
Yeah.

1:02:29.454 --> 1:02:30.789
Yeah, okay, thanks.

1:02:43.259 --> 1:02:44.886
(sighs)

1:02:48.765 --> 1:02:51.226
Hey, Susan.

1:02:51.226 --> 1:02:53.645
I'm so sorry.

1:02:53.645 --> 1:02:54.980
My mom called.

1:02:54.980 --> 1:02:57.607
I didn't have your dad's number.

1:02:57.607 --> 1:02:58.775
It's fine.

1:02:58.775 --> 1:03:01.736
You were right to worry.

1:03:01.736 --> 1:03:04.572
The foundation sent out
some help.

1:03:04.572 --> 1:03:06.658
♪

1:03:06.658 --> 1:03:08.952
Why don't I stay too?

1:03:08.952 --> 1:03:16.668
♪

1:03:16.668 --> 1:03:18.545
-What's going on?
-Nothing.

1:03:18.545 --> 1:03:20.839
Why did you say, "Holy shit"?

1:03:20.839 --> 1:03:22.799
It was Cherise.

1:03:22.799 --> 1:03:25.844
Her cousin Susan had an episode,
and, um, she wanted to warn you.

1:03:25.844 --> 1:03:27.387
What kind of episode?
Warn me, about what?

1:03:27.387 --> 1:03:29.472
She said not to trust
the foundation,

1:03:29.472 --> 1:03:32.183
that Susan has been feeding
her--her baby blood,

1:03:32.183 --> 1:03:34.144
and she pulled a knife
on Cherise.

1:03:34.144 --> 1:03:35.812
-Oh my God.
-She's okay, but--

1:03:35.812 --> 1:03:39.983
Postpartum depression can happen
in magical pregnancies too.

1:03:39.983 --> 1:03:43.319
It--it can make things
seem insurmountable, unreal.

1:03:43.319 --> 1:03:45.238
I'll have a pamphlet for you.

1:03:45.238 --> 1:03:47.490
Okay, but that doesn't explain
why she's--

1:03:47.490 --> 1:03:49.367
I'm sure someone
from the foundation

1:03:49.367 --> 1:03:51.077
is on their way
to help her out.

1:03:51.077 --> 1:03:53.246
They're the ones
behind all of this.

1:03:53.246 --> 1:03:54.748
What are they behind?

1:03:54.748 --> 1:03:56.041
Eric, what are you saying?

1:03:56.041 --> 1:03:58.376
Whatever you and Zekeny
are lying about, huh?

1:03:58.376 --> 1:03:59.878
I found out something
about the doctor.

1:03:59.878 --> 1:04:01.337
-He's lying about his age.
-Eric, come on.

1:04:01.337 --> 1:04:03.339
No, no, no, I want to know.

1:04:03.339 --> 1:04:05.216
I want to know the truth
about Zekeny,

1:04:05.216 --> 1:04:08.470
about our baby,
and about Susan.

1:04:08.470 --> 1:04:10.597
Is she crazy
or is she telling the truth

1:04:10.597 --> 1:04:12.766
about feeding her baby blood?

1:04:12.766 --> 1:04:14.642
♪

1:04:14.642 --> 1:04:17.020
Maybe sometimes a little, but--

1:04:17.020 --> 1:04:18.188
Are you fucking kidding me?

1:04:18.188 --> 1:04:20.106
Are we having
a fucking vampire baby?

1:04:20.106 --> 1:04:22.484
That term has
a lot of implications.

1:04:22.484 --> 1:04:23.985
Implications?

1:04:23.985 --> 1:04:25.236
What?!

1:04:25.236 --> 1:04:27.363
This is a person,

1:04:27.363 --> 1:04:29.074
just like you,

1:04:29.074 --> 1:04:31.701
with slightly unique needs.

1:04:31.701 --> 1:04:36.122
People eat placenta,
bone, brain.

1:04:36.122 --> 1:04:37.582
It's a monster.

1:04:37.582 --> 1:04:39.584
All babies are monsters.

1:04:39.584 --> 1:04:42.504
They--they scream and they cry
and they shit and they puke,

1:04:42.504 --> 1:04:46.633
but this one's ours, so--
so what should it matter?

1:04:46.633 --> 1:04:48.802
Susan tried to stab Cherise.

1:04:48.802 --> 1:04:50.053
Cherise, your best friend.

1:04:50.053 --> 1:04:51.888
That has nothing to do
with our baby.

1:04:51.888 --> 1:04:54.057
Yes, it does, obviously!

1:04:54.057 --> 1:04:56.059
♪

1:04:56.059 --> 1:04:57.769
Makayla!

1:04:57.769 --> 1:04:59.395
Back off!

1:04:59.395 --> 1:05:01.981
What are you hiding?

1:05:01.981 --> 1:05:06.402
What else could there
possibly be?

1:05:06.402 --> 1:05:09.072
Give me your phone.

1:05:09.072 --> 1:05:11.616
Give me the phone!

1:05:11.616 --> 1:05:13.785
Give her the damn phone!

1:05:13.785 --> 1:05:17.622
♪

1:05:17.622 --> 1:05:19.833
Finish painting.

1:05:19.833 --> 1:05:23.878
Think about what you're risking
if you screw this up.

1:05:23.878 --> 1:05:33.888
♪

1:05:36.516 --> 1:05:38.434
Did you get paint on your arm?

1:05:38.434 --> 1:05:40.353
-Yeah, sorry.
-Don't apologize,

1:05:40.353 --> 1:05:41.479
not your fault.

1:05:41.479 --> 1:05:42.814
I was distracted.

1:05:42.814 --> 1:05:43.815
Eric is...

1:05:43.815 --> 1:05:46.693
-All over the place?
-Exactly.

1:05:46.693 --> 1:05:48.236
Don't take it personally.

1:05:48.236 --> 1:05:50.947
Once he holds the baby,
he'll forget all about it.

1:05:50.947 --> 1:05:53.449
-I guess.
-I promise.

1:05:53.449 --> 1:05:56.536
Now, stay away
from the wet paint.

1:05:56.536 --> 1:05:59.205
Just one more ritual left.

1:05:59.205 --> 1:06:01.124
We don't want to mess it up.

1:06:01.124 --> 1:06:11.134
♪

1:06:20.393 --> 1:06:24.689
The young cat
looks to his mother,

1:06:24.689 --> 1:06:27.233
but she stays behind.

1:06:27.233 --> 1:06:29.611
Thanks for hanging out.

1:06:29.611 --> 1:06:31.613
Of course, anytime.

1:06:31.613 --> 1:06:34.490
He'll have to climb
this tray on his own.

1:06:34.490 --> 1:06:37.785
If my mom calls you,

1:06:37.785 --> 1:06:40.997
tell her I'm sleeping.

1:06:40.997 --> 1:06:43.541
Okay?

1:06:43.541 --> 1:06:45.919
Yeah, sure.

1:06:45.919 --> 1:06:55.929
♪

1:06:56.304 --> 1:06:58.056
Oops.

1:06:58.056 --> 1:07:00.808
Good thing it wasn't
too high up.

1:07:00.808 --> 1:07:03.269
He'll have to try again.

1:07:03.269 --> 1:07:05.063
This last ritual will ensure

1:07:05.063 --> 1:07:07.440
the vitality
of your child-to-be.

1:07:07.440 --> 1:07:10.151
Eric, you'll be chanting this.

1:07:10.151 --> 1:07:11.444
What does it mean?

1:07:11.444 --> 1:07:13.196
I can't tell you exactly.

1:07:13.196 --> 1:07:15.740
Just focus on how
it makes you feel.

1:07:15.740 --> 1:07:18.076
And at some point
during the ritual,

1:07:18.076 --> 1:07:19.619
it'll turn into English.

1:07:19.619 --> 1:07:22.747
♪

1:07:22.747 --> 1:07:27.460
If you stop, it would be
very, very dangerous.

1:07:27.460 --> 1:07:31.923
♪

1:07:31.923 --> 1:07:33.299
Go on.

1:07:33.299 --> 1:07:35.343
Um...

1:07:35.343 --> 1:07:39.347
(chanting in foreign language)

1:07:45.353 --> 1:07:47.438
(rumbling)

1:07:47.438 --> 1:07:48.815
This feels weird.

1:07:48.815 --> 1:07:50.817
(chanting continues)

1:07:54.779 --> 1:07:57.573
(groaning)

1:07:57.573 --> 1:07:59.325
I don't like this.

1:07:59.325 --> 1:08:01.327
Eric, Eric!

1:08:01.327 --> 1:08:03.663
Focus, Eric, focus!

1:08:03.663 --> 1:08:05.623
(groaning)

1:08:05.623 --> 1:08:08.042
-I forfeit my energy...
-It hurts, it hurts!

1:08:08.042 --> 1:08:09.377
...my person, myself.

1:08:09.377 --> 1:08:10.712
Let me go!

1:08:10.712 --> 1:08:13.756
I give it all away
to this, to you.

1:08:13.756 --> 1:08:15.675
(chanting continues)

1:08:15.675 --> 1:08:17.093
I forfeit my energy...

1:08:17.093 --> 1:08:20.096
-It's growing!
-...my person, myself.

1:08:20.096 --> 1:08:22.765
I give it all away
to this, to you.

1:08:22.765 --> 1:08:25.476
-Make it stop, make it stop!
-I forfeit my energy,

1:08:25.476 --> 1:08:27.603
-my person, myself.
-Help me!

1:08:27.603 --> 1:08:28.646
(screaming)

1:08:28.646 --> 1:08:32.150
I give it all away
to this, to you!

1:08:32.150 --> 1:08:36.112
(chanting continues)

1:08:36.112 --> 1:08:37.488
(sighs)

1:08:37.488 --> 1:08:38.740
♪

1:08:38.740 --> 1:08:40.366
Wonderful, Eric.

1:08:40.366 --> 1:08:48.166
♪

1:08:48.166 --> 1:08:49.500
Honey?

1:08:49.500 --> 1:08:53.129
♪

1:08:53.129 --> 1:08:54.797
We'll clean this up tomorrow.

1:08:54.797 --> 1:08:57.759
Turn out the candles
before you tuck in.

1:08:57.759 --> 1:09:02.221
The doctor will be here
sometime overnight.

1:09:02.221 --> 1:09:04.849
Sleep well.

1:09:04.849 --> 1:09:07.185
I'm...so sorry.

1:09:07.185 --> 1:09:08.311
(groans)

1:09:08.311 --> 1:09:10.188
Why are you sorry?

1:09:10.188 --> 1:09:12.315
♪

1:09:12.315 --> 1:09:16.486
You were begging and screaming,
and I said, uh...

1:09:16.486 --> 1:09:18.279
those words.

1:09:18.279 --> 1:09:20.156
They're just words.

1:09:20.156 --> 1:09:24.285
Just a way to access the magic.

1:09:24.285 --> 1:09:26.287
But they felt true.

1:09:26.287 --> 1:09:29.874
They're supposed to be.

1:09:29.874 --> 1:09:33.419
And there was this thing,
and it was in my chest,

1:09:33.419 --> 1:09:35.296
and I couldn't keep it in.

1:09:35.296 --> 1:09:37.882
That's love.

1:09:37.882 --> 1:09:39.717
That's how I feel
about the person

1:09:39.717 --> 1:09:43.137
that's growing inside of me.

1:09:43.137 --> 1:09:45.932
But it was--it was...

1:09:45.932 --> 1:09:47.558
It didn't feel like love.

1:09:47.558 --> 1:09:49.185
It was, um...

1:09:49.185 --> 1:09:51.604
♪

1:09:51.604 --> 1:09:54.399
It was terrifying.

1:09:54.399 --> 1:09:58.152
It's supposed to be.

1:09:58.152 --> 1:09:59.946
Here.

1:09:59.946 --> 1:10:03.324
♪

1:10:03.324 --> 1:10:06.160
Just wait.

1:10:06.160 --> 1:10:08.079
It'll come.

1:10:08.079 --> 1:10:11.749
♪

1:10:11.749 --> 1:10:13.459
(chuckling)

1:10:13.459 --> 1:10:23.469
♪

1:10:25.263 --> 1:10:27.932
(crickets chirring)

1:10:27.932 --> 1:10:37.942
♪

1:10:42.029 --> 1:10:44.031
(door closes)

1:10:44.031 --> 1:10:53.124
♪

1:10:53.124 --> 1:10:54.625
Lots of kicking.

1:10:54.625 --> 1:10:57.086
(ultrasound whirring)

1:10:57.086 --> 1:11:00.840
Just trying to find
the heartbeat.

1:11:00.840 --> 1:11:03.468
I saw a picture of your father.

1:11:03.468 --> 1:11:05.803
A handsome fellow.

1:11:10.308 --> 1:11:12.477
Is it right that our baby
will drink blood?

1:11:12.477 --> 1:11:14.187
-Eric, what are you doing?
-I'm just asking.

1:11:14.187 --> 1:11:15.605
You're just trying
to find a problem.

1:11:15.605 --> 1:11:18.065
-No, I'm not...
-He's just anxious.

1:11:18.065 --> 1:11:21.194
All guys go through it
as it gets closer.

1:11:21.194 --> 1:11:23.112
He's going through a lot too.

1:11:23.112 --> 1:11:25.406
Yeah, but...

1:11:25.406 --> 1:11:28.075
I know, but still,

1:11:28.075 --> 1:11:30.620
it's a process.

1:11:30.620 --> 1:11:33.456
My dad, on the day I was born,
drank a bottle of whiskey

1:11:33.456 --> 1:11:35.833
and threw up
on the accoucheur.

1:11:35.833 --> 1:11:39.545
(ultrasound pulsing)

1:11:39.545 --> 1:11:41.088
Right.

1:11:41.088 --> 1:11:44.425
The, uh, midwife.

1:11:44.425 --> 1:11:46.093
Anyway...

1:11:46.093 --> 1:11:48.054
(ultrasound whirring)

1:11:50.473 --> 1:11:54.060
The heartbeat.

1:11:54.060 --> 1:11:56.521
Nice and healthy.

1:11:56.521 --> 1:11:57.813
(high-pitched sound)

1:11:57.813 --> 1:11:59.857
Whoa.

1:11:59.857 --> 1:12:01.150
A little too loud.

1:12:01.150 --> 1:12:02.777
(sighs)

1:12:05.488 --> 1:12:07.615
(sighs, chuckles)

1:12:13.871 --> 1:12:18.459
♪

1:12:18.459 --> 1:12:20.044
(groans)

1:12:20.044 --> 1:12:30.054
♪

1:12:37.645 --> 1:12:40.648
(chanting in foreign language)

1:12:45.444 --> 1:12:47.488
Morning.

1:12:47.488 --> 1:12:51.784
♪

1:12:51.784 --> 1:12:53.494
(soft chuckle)

1:12:53.494 --> 1:12:59.250
♪

1:12:59.250 --> 1:13:01.752
(water running)

1:13:01.752 --> 1:13:11.762
♪

1:13:14.515 --> 1:13:17.018
(breathing heavily)

1:13:17.018 --> 1:13:27.028
♪

1:13:36.495 --> 1:13:38.122
(laughing)

1:13:38.122 --> 1:13:48.132
♪

1:14:55.783 --> 1:14:57.994
(clattering)

1:14:57.994 --> 1:15:06.585
♪

1:15:06.585 --> 1:15:08.212
Don't move.

1:15:08.212 --> 1:15:18.222
♪

1:15:23.853 --> 1:15:25.646
(moans)

1:15:25.646 --> 1:15:28.107
(wood clacking)

1:15:28.107 --> 1:15:29.233
Ow, Jesus!

1:15:29.233 --> 1:15:31.902
-Come now.
-What, what's wrong?

1:15:31.902 --> 1:15:34.989
(music box playing)

1:15:34.989 --> 1:15:40.202
♪

1:15:40.202 --> 1:15:42.997
(birds chirping)

1:15:42.997 --> 1:15:53.007
♪

1:16:10.065 --> 1:16:11.817
Susan?

1:16:11.817 --> 1:16:21.827
♪

1:16:28.834 --> 1:16:30.461
Susan?

1:16:30.461 --> 1:16:40.471
♪

1:16:49.104 --> 1:16:50.689
Susan?

1:16:50.689 --> 1:17:00.699
♪

1:17:02.159 --> 1:17:04.245
(door creaking)

1:17:04.245 --> 1:17:14.255
♪

1:17:40.990 --> 1:17:43.325
Your blood seeped into her skin,

1:17:43.325 --> 1:17:45.160
and now...that...

1:17:45.160 --> 1:17:46.745
What the fuck is that?

1:17:46.745 --> 1:17:48.372
I don't know what it is.

1:17:48.372 --> 1:17:49.707
I'll make a poultice

1:17:49.707 --> 1:17:51.125
and call the doctor.

1:17:51.125 --> 1:17:52.918
Help her to the bedroom.

1:17:52.918 --> 1:17:56.881
♪

1:17:56.881 --> 1:17:58.465
Not that hand.

1:17:58.465 --> 1:18:02.386
♪

1:18:02.386 --> 1:18:04.388
(phone vibrating)

1:18:04.388 --> 1:18:11.437
♪

1:18:11.437 --> 1:18:13.188
Draw this.

1:18:13.188 --> 1:18:15.733
A triangle pointing up
right around the spot.

1:18:15.733 --> 1:18:20.529
Then wipe it off
and do it again and again.

1:18:20.529 --> 1:18:22.406
That should keep it
from spreading.

1:18:22.406 --> 1:18:24.533
Is she okay?

1:18:24.533 --> 1:18:26.076
I'm calling the doctor again.

1:18:26.076 --> 1:18:29.330
They said he was sleeping,
but he has to get up for this.

1:18:29.330 --> 1:18:30.998
(door opens)

1:18:33.042 --> 1:18:34.793
(door closes)

1:18:35.878 --> 1:18:37.630
(sighs)

1:18:37.630 --> 1:18:40.674
♪

1:18:40.674 --> 1:18:42.676
My client has an infection
or something.

1:18:42.676 --> 1:18:44.261
I don't know what it is.

1:18:44.261 --> 1:18:45.930
Yes, that's why I called.

1:18:45.930 --> 1:18:47.139
Just wake him up!

1:18:47.139 --> 1:18:48.724
(birds chirping)

1:18:48.724 --> 1:18:50.017
(knocking furiously)

1:18:50.017 --> 1:18:51.936
Makayla, Eric, let me in!

1:18:51.936 --> 1:18:53.187
(knocking)

1:18:53.187 --> 1:18:55.940
♪

1:18:55.940 --> 1:18:57.441
Why are you stopping?

1:18:57.441 --> 1:18:59.193
She sounds scared.

1:18:59.193 --> 1:19:00.986
What about the baby?

1:19:00.986 --> 1:19:02.488
I'll be right back.

1:19:02.488 --> 1:19:07.117
♪

1:19:07.117 --> 1:19:08.244
Come on.

1:19:08.244 --> 1:19:10.913
Makayla, Eric!
Where are you?

1:19:10.913 --> 1:19:13.582
-Who are you? Shoo, shoo!
-Cherise?

1:19:13.582 --> 1:19:17.378
-Stop! Eric, stop her, stop her!
-The bedroom.

1:19:17.378 --> 1:19:19.505
Cherise,
what are you doing here?

1:19:19.505 --> 1:19:21.465
-Come with me.
-No, what's happening?

1:19:21.465 --> 1:19:23.050
She is dangerous!

1:19:23.050 --> 1:19:24.551
They are dangerous!

1:19:24.551 --> 1:19:26.887
Makayla, you don't know
what's growing inside of you.

1:19:26.887 --> 1:19:27.930
A baby!

1:19:27.930 --> 1:19:29.181
A beautiful baby.

1:19:29.181 --> 1:19:30.808
Susan is dead!

1:19:30.808 --> 1:19:33.102
She killed herself
and her baby.

1:19:33.102 --> 1:19:34.520
I saw.

1:19:34.520 --> 1:19:36.814
I saw them in the bathroom.

1:19:36.814 --> 1:19:40.317
♪

1:19:40.317 --> 1:19:43.988
She took pills, and--
and the baby was in the tub.

1:19:43.988 --> 1:19:47.700
♪

1:19:47.700 --> 1:19:49.368
The baby...

1:19:49.368 --> 1:19:51.996
(sobbing)

1:19:51.996 --> 1:19:53.497
♪

1:19:53.497 --> 1:19:55.582
It wasn't a baby.

1:19:55.582 --> 1:19:58.419
♪

1:19:58.419 --> 1:20:00.004
What--what was it?

1:20:00.004 --> 1:20:04.299
♪

1:20:04.299 --> 1:20:06.176
Inhuman.

1:20:06.176 --> 1:20:11.598
♪

1:20:11.598 --> 1:20:12.891
What does that mean?

1:20:12.891 --> 1:20:16.061
It had claws, she fed it blood.

1:20:16.061 --> 1:20:17.271
-We know.
-Claws?

1:20:17.271 --> 1:20:18.731
-Makayla, let's go.
-Ouch.

1:20:18.731 --> 1:20:20.899
-We gotta get you out of here!
-No, no, no!

1:20:20.899 --> 1:20:22.526
-Let go of her!
-Stop pulling her!

1:20:22.526 --> 1:20:24.570
-Ow!
-How do you think this happens?

1:20:24.570 --> 1:20:26.030
This is not natural!

1:20:26.030 --> 1:20:28.032
-Cherise, you don't know that.
-No, it's not natural...

1:20:28.032 --> 1:20:30.200
They were controlling Susan,
threatening her!

1:20:30.200 --> 1:20:32.202
-Helping her.
-This is different.

1:20:32.202 --> 1:20:34.788
She couldn't handle being
a mother; I'm meant for this.

1:20:34.788 --> 1:20:37.458
Makayla, your baby
is an abomination.

1:20:37.458 --> 1:20:39.877
Cherise, how could--
how could you say that?

1:20:39.877 --> 1:20:41.587
Please, you have to believe me.

1:20:41.587 --> 1:20:42.880
I'm trying to save her.

1:20:42.880 --> 1:20:45.507
Cherise, I--I think--
I think you should go.

1:20:45.507 --> 1:20:46.842
What?

1:20:46.842 --> 1:20:50.554
(Makayla panting)

1:20:50.554 --> 1:20:52.598
I'm sorry, I can't.

1:20:52.598 --> 1:20:55.392
(growling, screaming)

1:20:55.392 --> 1:20:58.020
(guttural growling)

1:20:58.020 --> 1:21:00.189
Zekeny, what are you doing?
Get off her, let her--

1:21:00.189 --> 1:21:01.482
Eric!

1:21:01.482 --> 1:21:03.734
(panting)

1:21:03.734 --> 1:21:07.654
(growling, choking)

1:21:07.654 --> 1:21:09.615
Get out!

1:21:09.615 --> 1:21:11.784
(gasping)

1:21:11.784 --> 1:21:12.993
Wait.

1:21:12.993 --> 1:21:15.996
(panting)

1:21:15.996 --> 1:21:18.874
-We might need her.
-Need her for what?

1:21:18.874 --> 1:21:21.668
(Cherise gasping)

1:21:21.668 --> 1:21:23.921
Get the rope.

1:21:23.921 --> 1:21:26.632
(panting)

1:21:26.632 --> 1:21:28.175
♪

1:21:28.175 --> 1:21:29.551
I can't...

1:21:29.551 --> 1:21:31.512
Wait, wait, wait, wait.

1:21:31.512 --> 1:21:32.888
What's happening?

1:21:32.888 --> 1:21:33.972
(muffled scream)

1:21:33.972 --> 1:21:35.349
Zekeny, what are you doing?

1:21:35.349 --> 1:21:36.600
(snarls)

1:21:36.600 --> 1:21:40.562
(muffled screaming)

1:21:40.562 --> 1:21:42.940
(screaming stops)

1:21:42.940 --> 1:21:45.275
(panting)

1:21:45.275 --> 1:21:54.201
♪

1:21:54.201 --> 1:21:56.453
Your baby is sensitive to blood.

1:21:56.453 --> 1:21:58.872
You said the licking was fine.

1:21:58.872 --> 1:22:01.083
That was her blood.

1:22:01.083 --> 1:22:05.170
But yours, when it got
on the skin and it stayed there,

1:22:05.170 --> 1:22:07.714
it caused the magic, the energy

1:22:07.714 --> 1:22:11.969
that needs to be contained
in the baby, to leak.

1:22:11.969 --> 1:22:14.805
Your body is not meant
for magic.

1:22:14.805 --> 1:22:18.016
I can heal you, but the medicine
is bad for the baby.

1:22:18.016 --> 1:22:19.685
-Cherise!
-Pay attention.

1:22:19.685 --> 1:22:21.895
We need to induce labor now

1:22:21.895 --> 1:22:25.691
or you could lose your wife
and your baby.

1:22:25.691 --> 1:22:27.734
You gonna let me?

1:22:27.734 --> 1:22:30.487
(panting)

1:22:32.573 --> 1:22:33.907
Yeah.

1:22:33.907 --> 1:22:35.909
(panting)

1:22:35.909 --> 1:22:37.619
-Save them.
-All right.

1:22:37.619 --> 1:22:40.038
(chanting in foreign language)

1:22:40.038 --> 1:22:45.210
♪

1:22:45.210 --> 1:22:47.880
(screaming)

1:22:47.880 --> 1:22:50.757
Get ready for the big ones
but don't push yet.

1:22:50.757 --> 1:22:52.551
(screaming)

1:22:52.551 --> 1:22:54.469
(panting, exhaling)

1:22:54.469 --> 1:22:55.512
(screaming)

1:22:55.512 --> 1:22:56.847
You got this, honey.

1:22:56.847 --> 1:22:59.183
You can do it.

1:22:59.183 --> 1:23:01.810
(screaming)

1:23:01.810 --> 1:23:06.899
♪

1:23:06.899 --> 1:23:09.193
Hang in there, sweetie.

1:23:09.193 --> 1:23:10.527
It's okay.

1:23:10.527 --> 1:23:12.529
It's okay. It's okay.

1:23:12.529 --> 1:23:14.823
(screaming)

1:23:14.823 --> 1:23:16.825
♪

1:23:16.825 --> 1:23:19.286
All right, next time you feel
a contraction coming...

1:23:19.286 --> 1:23:22.497
-Breathe, sweetie, breathe.
-...push as hard as you can.

1:23:22.497 --> 1:23:24.958
(screaming)

1:23:24.958 --> 1:23:31.590
♪

1:23:31.590 --> 1:23:33.467
Push, push!

1:23:33.467 --> 1:23:35.677
(screaming)

1:23:35.677 --> 1:23:42.142
♪

1:23:42.142 --> 1:23:43.518
There she is.

1:23:43.518 --> 1:23:45.938
I got her.

1:23:45.938 --> 1:23:47.606
It's a girl.

1:23:47.606 --> 1:23:50.817
♪

1:23:50.817 --> 1:23:52.653
It's okay.

1:23:52.653 --> 1:23:54.279
(panting)

1:23:54.279 --> 1:23:56.031
Ola,

1:23:56.031 --> 1:23:57.282
we have a problem.

1:23:57.282 --> 1:23:59.493
You need to drink this
before anything else.

1:23:59.493 --> 1:24:01.620
-What's wrong?
-It's medicine, drink it.

1:24:01.620 --> 1:24:03.497
-Is she okay?
-We have to be fast.

1:24:03.497 --> 1:24:05.290
What's going on?

1:24:05.290 --> 1:24:06.875
She should be crying.

1:24:06.875 --> 1:24:09.544
Why isn't she crying?
What's happening?

1:24:09.544 --> 1:24:11.171
Why isn't she crying?

1:24:11.171 --> 1:24:12.756
She's barely hanging on.

1:24:12.756 --> 1:24:15.092
What--what is happening?

1:24:15.092 --> 1:24:17.678
An infection,
from Eric's blood.

1:24:17.678 --> 1:24:19.221
(crying)

1:24:19.221 --> 1:24:20.847
You did this!

1:24:20.847 --> 1:24:24.685
It's your fault,
it's all your fault!

1:24:24.685 --> 1:24:26.895
I'm sorry. I'm sorry!

1:24:26.895 --> 1:24:28.897
You...

1:24:28.897 --> 1:24:30.148
I'm sorry.

1:24:30.148 --> 1:24:31.483
(crying)

1:24:31.483 --> 1:24:34.278
I didn't mean it,
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

1:24:34.278 --> 1:24:35.779
(crying)

1:24:35.779 --> 1:24:37.823
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

1:24:37.823 --> 1:24:38.865
Get off!

1:24:38.865 --> 1:24:41.118
There's still a chance
we can fix it,

1:24:41.118 --> 1:24:43.620
but it's big, costly magic,

1:24:43.620 --> 1:24:45.706
not the kind of thing
the foundation does

1:24:45.706 --> 1:24:48.083
-without total commitment.
-Put me down! Get off!

1:24:48.083 --> 1:24:51.086
You have to supply the main
component for the spell.

1:24:51.086 --> 1:24:53.338
Yes, of course, what is it?

1:24:53.338 --> 1:24:55.716
♪

1:24:55.716 --> 1:24:58.302
A fresh human heart.

1:24:58.302 --> 1:25:00.178
♪

1:25:00.178 --> 1:25:03.682
Why are you looking at me?
What's she talking about?

1:25:03.682 --> 1:25:04.766
No.

1:25:04.766 --> 1:25:06.143
No, no way, no.

1:25:06.143 --> 1:25:08.562
I understand.

1:25:08.562 --> 1:25:10.647
It's your choice,

1:25:10.647 --> 1:25:13.066
but there are no second chances.

1:25:13.066 --> 1:25:16.403
♪

1:25:16.403 --> 1:25:17.404
Eric.

1:25:17.404 --> 1:25:19.531
We're not gonna murder
our friend.

1:25:19.531 --> 1:25:21.033
♪

1:25:21.033 --> 1:25:22.367
Eric.

1:25:22.367 --> 1:25:27.080
♪

1:25:27.080 --> 1:25:29.666
Please.

1:25:29.666 --> 1:25:32.252
This is our only chance.

1:25:32.252 --> 1:25:35.422
This is my only chance!

1:25:35.422 --> 1:25:38.592
I love you, and I want
to do this with you.

1:25:38.592 --> 1:25:40.218
Please.

1:25:40.218 --> 1:25:42.888
I need this baby.

1:25:42.888 --> 1:25:46.141
If you're willing
to murder your friend,

1:25:46.141 --> 1:25:47.726
for that...

1:25:47.726 --> 1:25:50.270
♪

1:25:50.270 --> 1:25:53.440
...maybe you're not fit
to be a mother.

1:25:53.440 --> 1:25:57.402
♪

1:25:57.402 --> 1:25:59.404
Get the fuck outta here!

1:25:59.404 --> 1:26:00.655
Get!

1:26:00.655 --> 1:26:03.367
(panting)

1:26:03.367 --> 1:26:08.121
♪

1:26:08.121 --> 1:26:11.583
-Eric, Eric.
-It's okay, it's okay.

1:26:11.583 --> 1:26:13.210
A heart?

1:26:13.210 --> 1:26:23.220
♪

1:26:26.765 --> 1:26:28.350
What the fuck is going on?

1:26:28.350 --> 1:26:29.643
(smacks)

1:26:29.643 --> 1:26:31.937
♪

1:26:31.937 --> 1:26:34.523
(smacking)

1:26:34.523 --> 1:26:38.652
♪

1:26:38.652 --> 1:26:41.071
Enough, enough!

1:26:41.071 --> 1:26:43.490
(panting)

1:26:43.490 --> 1:26:46.910
♪

1:26:46.910 --> 1:26:48.787
Wait for instructions.

1:26:48.787 --> 1:26:50.330
♪

1:26:50.330 --> 1:26:52.457
(choking on blood)

1:26:52.457 --> 1:26:54.501
Let me flip him over.

1:26:54.501 --> 1:26:58.463
♪

1:26:58.463 --> 1:26:59.631
Cut down.

1:26:59.631 --> 1:27:02.968
(slicing)

1:27:02.968 --> 1:27:05.846
(gasping)

1:27:05.846 --> 1:27:07.431
Cut through there.

1:27:07.431 --> 1:27:10.058
(slicing, grunting)

1:27:10.058 --> 1:27:12.436
♪

1:27:12.436 --> 1:27:15.313
Now give me the knife, reach in.

1:27:15.313 --> 1:27:17.357
♪

1:27:17.357 --> 1:27:19.025
(squelching)

1:27:19.025 --> 1:27:24.072
♪

1:27:24.072 --> 1:27:26.158
(Cherise whimpering)

1:27:26.158 --> 1:27:27.451
♪

1:27:27.451 --> 1:27:29.661
(Cherise gasping)

1:27:29.661 --> 1:27:36.209
♪

1:27:36.209 --> 1:27:37.669
Squeeze.

1:27:37.669 --> 1:27:39.463
Take this life as your own.

1:27:39.463 --> 1:27:41.256
May it sustain you.

1:27:41.256 --> 1:27:45.802
Take this life as your own,
may it sustain you.

1:27:45.802 --> 1:27:48.054
(baby crying)

1:27:48.054 --> 1:27:57.647
♪

1:27:57.647 --> 1:27:59.941
What about the friend?

1:27:59.941 --> 1:28:02.569
Let me handle her.

1:28:02.569 --> 1:28:04.112
(growling)

1:28:04.112 --> 1:28:06.448
(biting, screaming)

